wiki.article.standard.roleSetGraveKiller:
Role Set Grave Killers is a game modifier that changes the game such that every grave killer which is a role is replaced with one of:
* Syndicate;
* Town;
* Minions;
* Neutral;
* Fiends; or
* Cult.

Or, if the killer's role is not in one of these role sets, it is not changed.
